name: TT1-A - ApeChad to the Moon - Burn Up Edition
description: The massive speed of ApeChad's rocket only increases the friction even in the thin atmosphere. Temps rise inside ApeChad's suit and they can smell their hair starting to burn! Can ApeChad make it to orbit or will the blistering speed of the TezTools rocket rip ApeChad asunder and scatter his remains through the planet's atmosphere?
